      <tag>spiritual song</tag>
    </tags>
    <melody>Hoe lustelijk is ons de koele mei gedaan</melody>
  </meta>
  <text>
    <lg type="song">
      <lg id="s1" type="stanza">
        <l id="s1:l1" met="5" type="-+">Hoe schone ende ghenoegelijc is ons des crucen mey <rhyme label="a" type="m">ghedaen</rhyme></l>
        <l id="s1:l2" met="5" type="-+">Het spruyten ghelu bloemkens aender groender <rhyme label="b" type="f">heyden</rhyme></l>
        <l id="s1:l3" met="5" type="-+">So wie met druck met liden is <rhyme label="a" type="m" corresp="#s1:l1">beuaen</rhyme></l>
        <l id="s1:l4" met="6" type="-+">In Iesus wonden mach hi hem gaen vermeyden <rhyme label="b" type="f" corresp="#s1:l2">vermeyden</rhyme></l>
      </lg>
      <lg id="s2" type="stanza">
        <l id="s2:l1" met="5" type="-+">Die mey die is al biden wech <rhyme label="a" type="m">gheset</rhyme></l>
        <l id="s2:l2" met="5" type="-+">Op eenen berch ende die staet alsoe <rhyme label="b" type="f">hoghen</rhyme></l>
        <l id="s2:l3" met="5" type="-+">Om dat een yeghelijc soude sonder <rhyme label="a" type="m" corresp="#s2:l1">let</rhyme></l>
        <l id="s2:l4" met="6" type="-+">Den soeten cruycen meye aenscouwen <rhyme label="b" type="f" corresp="#s2:l2">moghen</rhyme>.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg id="s3" type="stanza">
        <l id="s3:l1" met="5" type="-+">Nu siet des meyen tacken wt <rhyme label="a" type="m">ghespreyt</rhyme></l>
        <l id="s3:l2" met="5" type="-+">Ende bloyen schoon ghelijck die roode <rhyme label="b" type="f">roosen</rhyme></l>
        <l id="s3:l3" met="5" type="-+">So wie sijn sonden sijn gebreken hier <rhyme label="a" type="m" corresp="#s3:l1">bescreyt</rhyme></l>
        <l id="s3:l4" met="6" type="-+">Onder desen boom so sal hi hem <rhyme label="b" type="f" corresp="#s3:l2">verpoosen</rhyme>.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg id="s4" type="stanza">
        <l id="s4:l1" met="5" type="-+">Recht op ghewassen so is den edelen <rhyme label="a" type="m">greyn</rhyme></l>
        <l id="s4:l2" met="5" type="-+">Ende is gheplant in also diepen <rhyme label="b" type="f">dale</rhyme></l>
        <l id="s4:l3" met="5" type="-+">Dat is in Maria die suuer maget <rhyme label="a" type="m" corresp="#s4:l1">reyn</rhyme></l>
        <l id="s4:l4" met="6" type="-+">Van minnen soe sterf die fiere <rhyme label="b" type="f" corresp="#s4:l2">nachtegale</rhyme>.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg id="s5" type="stanza">
        <l id="s5:l1" met="5" type="-+">Die fiere nachtegale des crucen boom op <rhyme label="a" type="m">clam</rhyme></l>
        <l id="s5:l2" met="5" type="-+">Hi heeft sijn vederkens also wide <rhyme label="b" type="f">ontploken</rhyme></l>
        <l id="s5:l3" met="5" type="-+">Hi sanck soe luyde die seuen noten <rhyme label="a" type="m" corresp="#s5:l1">hooch</rhyme></l>
        <l id="s5:l4" met="6" type="-+">Soe dat sijn edele hertken is <rhyme label="b" type="f" corresp="#s5:l2">ghebroken</rhyme></l>
      </lg>
      <lg id="s6" type="stanza">
        <l id="s6:l1" met="5" type="-+">Nu is die fiere nachtegale bleuen <rhyme label="a" type="m">doot</rhyme></l>
        <l id="s6:l2" met="5" type="-+">Om die minnen van eender suyuere <rhyme label="b" type="f">ioncfrouwen</rhyme></l>
        <l id="s6:l3" met="5" type="-+">Hi quam so hooghe al wt sijns vaders <rhyme label="a" type="m" corresp="#s6:l1">schoot</rhyme></l>
        <l id="s6:l4" met="6" type="-+">Wie hoorde ye ghelijcke deser <rhyme label="b" type="f" corresp="#s6:l2">trouwen</rhyme>.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg id="s7" type="stanza">
        <l id="s7:l1" met="5" type="-+">So wien sijn sinnen noch onghestadich <rhyme label="a" type="m">sijn</rhyme></l>
        <l id="s7:l2" met="5" type="-+">Ende cleuen noch op aertsche <rhyme label="b" type="f">creaturen</rhyme></l>
        <l id="s7:l3" met="5" type="-+">Die aenmercke dese edelen nachtegael <rhyme label="a" type="m" corresp="#s7:l1">fijn</rhyme></l>
        <l id="s7:l4" met="6" type="-+">Hoe hi den doot om onsen wil wouode <rhyme label="b" type="f" corresp="#s7:l2">besueren</rhyme>.</l>
      </lg>
    </lg>
  </text>
</song>
